1) ALWAYS have KEI.  stay bound in nexus or baazar (sp?) and there will usually be a 60 chanter there.  Give him/her about 75pp, if they're really nice they'll do it for free.  Always offer to create foci for him/her too.<br>
2) go to KC.  from 51-53, summon your 51 VE.  BO him, DS him, and park him at entrance, right where you zone in.  mem malisement, pull with that.  PULL ALL THE WAY BACK TO YOUR PET.  If you pull with any kind of damage dealer, the dogs/skeles/ghosts will get a few good licks in on ya before the pet gets argo.<br>
3) everything from 51-54 will be deep blue.  you can not single pull until 55, so make sure there are no other mobs close till you are 55.<br>
4) at 54 use your water pet.  faster hp regen for pet, bs comes in handy, and youll have a quicker kill rate.<br>
5) at 55 becomes incredibly easy.  75% are dark blue.  pull with malisement, DoT with wraith, Sirocco at 50% health.<br>
<br>
there it is, as simple as I can put it.  You dont want to do that, tough marbles, then this isnt for you.  To everyone else, goodluck! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uyanbun.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yanbun</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 231<br> <font color=#333333>(7/11/02 3:56:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=249.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 51-57, its really easy to do solo</span><hr size=1> Note - KC is Noob trainsville on my server. <p>"History is just a set of lies agreed upon" - Emperor Napoleon Bonaparte
